PROJECT OF AGENDA

Project: Agenda Auditorium for Jorge Basadre Grohmann National University

This project was build in Vue.js and Laravel framework with voyager. I build this project for my portfolio and my university like practice.

Link to Project

http://www.agenda.unjbg.edu.pe/

Github Frontend

Github Backend

User Stories

  1. I build this project for my university.

  2. I GET information about activities in UNJBG to http://www.agenda.unjbg.edu.pe

  3. I GET to http://www.agenda.unjbg.edu.pe/api/activities and I will receive a list of activities for university. Example :

    {
    "data": [
        {
        "id": 5,
        "description": null,
        "hour_initial": "09:00 am",
        "hour_end": "11:00 am.",
        "title": "Autodiagnostico de RSU Actividad a cargo de DARSU",
        "date": "2018-10-02"
        }
    ],
    "links": {
    "meta": {
    }
}
